finding: Section: "Diagnosis and Treatment of Feline Herpesvirus Type 1 (FHV-1) Infection"
Context: Description of a feline herpesvirus type 1 (FHV-1) infection in a tiger in a zoo in China.
c) The study also found that the virus was highly similar to those of other animal species, including canine herpesvirus (CHV) and equine herpesvirus (EHV).
